videos.description: Despite the small flaws, Florida head coach Dan Mullen believes the tight ends stepped up and QB Kyle Trask had a solid game.
videos.headline: Mullen puts perfection aside to commend his team

videos.description: No. 6 Florida QB Kyle Trask says his focus is week-to-week as Gator fans anoint him with Heisman cheers after a terrific six-touchdown performance.
videos.headline: Trask remains humble as Heisman cheers rise

videos.description: No. 6 Florida QB Kyle Trask becomes the first Gator to pass for 6 TDs in multiple games with the 63-35 win over Arkansas.
videos.headline: Trask's 6-TD day helps Florida bypass Arkansas
